uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.alignment

Class ObiwarpHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.alignment.ObiwarpHelper

  • public class ObiwarpHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class for the Obiwarp task. The class provides methods to generate mz bins from the list of profiles to be aligned and convert ProfileContainer into lmata files.
